# Deployment

- **Deploy only via SSH SCP.** Do not use FTP, rsync, or other methods unless the user explicitly asks.
- **Staging server:**
  - Host: `u816973857@145.79.211.86`
  - Port: `65002`
  - Base path: `~/domains/nutanvij.com/public_html/staging/`
- **SCP pattern** (run from project root):
  ```bash
  cd /Users/rutvikkorat/StudioProjects/smart_attendance_tracker && \
  sshpass -p "Korat@2511" scp -P 65002 \
    -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -o ConnectTimeout=120 \
    -o ServerAliveInterval=30 -o ServerAliveCountMax=6 \
    <local_path> \
    u816973857@145.79.211.86:<remote_path>
